==== 上帝模擬遊戲 ====
{{main|上帝模擬遊戲}}
玩家可以在該類遊戲的擁有一定的能力，例如飾演古希臘神話角色。<ref name="fundamentals"/>玩家的力量來自於虛構的信仰，通常是崇拜自然的部落信仰。<ref name="fundamentals"/>玩家要妥善利用他們的法力或力量，它們通常來自於信仰的人口數或繁榮度。<ref name="fundamentals"/>

上帝模擬遊戲是生命模擬遊戲的子分類，遊戲裡玩家只能間接操控生命，<ref name="fundamentals"/>這點與其他生命模擬遊戲、建設模擬遊戲及[[即時戰略|即時戰略]]遊戲有所不同<ref name="fundamentals"/>。玩家不能控制部隊的行動，即使多人遊戲模式亦是如此。<ref name="fundamentals"/>此外，玩家可以透過神力獲得其他建設及管理遊戲中不會出現的能力，例如控制天氣、改變地型或者透過祈禱改變人口。<ref name="fundamentals"/>

=== 社交模擬遊戲 ===
{{main|社會模擬遊戲}}
社交模擬遊戲是模擬人工生命體互動的遊戲。最著名的例子是《[[模拟人生_(游戏)|模擬市民]]》，<ref name=itconversations>{{cite web | last = Wright | first = Will | title = Presentation: Sculpting Possibility Space | url = http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail376.html | accessdate = 2008-03-16 | archive-date = 2007-10-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071013155032/http://itc.conversationsnetwork.org/shows/detail376.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>這個遊戲受到1985年遊戲《[[Little_Computer_People|Little Computer People]]》所影響。<ref name=willwrightinterview>{{cite web | last =Wright | first =Will | title =A chat about the "The Sims" and "SimCity" | publisher =[[CNN|CNN]] | url =http://www.cnn.com/chat/transcripts/2000/1/wright/index.html | accessdate =2008-03-18 | archive-date =2000-03-03 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20000303231358/http://www.cnn.com/chat/transcripts/2000/1/wright/index.html | dead-url =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/little-computer-people-review | publisher = Eurogamer | title = Little Computer People Review | access-date = 2011-06-22 | archive-date = 2020-05-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200502170616/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/little-computer-people-review | dead-url = no }}</ref>這類遊戲是人工生命遊戲的子分類的一部分，有時候被稱為虛擬娃娃屋，<ref name="fundamentals"/>其中包含[[任天堂|任天堂]]製作的《[[動物森友會|動物森友會]]》。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://cube.gamespy.com/articles/639/639689p15.html | title = GameSpy: Top 25 Games of All Time | publisher = GameSpy | access-date = 2011-06-22 | archive-date = 2011-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110906035344/http://cube.gamespy.com/articles/639/639689p15.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

